---
/**
 * Aurora Background Component - Galactic Tide Theme v4.0
 *
 * Starlight Commentary:
 * Monotonous auroras cannot embody the grandeur and flux of "tidal" motion.
 * We upgrade Aurora.astro into a multi-layered, asynchronous, color-rich system.
 * Three independent div layers, each applying different aurora-flow animations
 * defined in global.css. Each layer consists of multiple radial-gradients with
 * varying colors and sizes. This layered, asynchronous animation, combined with
 * richer color palettes, creates a truly organic, flowing, never-repeating
 * aurora tidal effect.
 *
 * Engineering Note:
 * -z-10 places the aurora above the starfield (-z-20), creating a foreground glow.
 * The three divs represent distinct color and motion layers. They use different
 * animations (aurora-flow-1/2/3) and durations (80s, 70s, 60s). This asynchrony
 * is key to creating organic visual rhythm.
 */
---

<div aria-hidden="true" class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-full -z-10 opacity-60 dark:opacity-40 pointer-events-none">
  <!-- Layer 1: Base Sea Tones -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0"
    style="background-image:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 20%, var(--color-sea-surface) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 80%, var(--color-sea-deep) 0%, transparent 50%);
      animation: aurora-flow-1 80s linear infinite;"
  ></div>

  <!-- Layer 2: Nebula & Stardust Accents -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0"
    style="background-image:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 40% 40%, var(--color-nebula-magenta) 0%, transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 60%, var(--color-nebula-violet) 0%, transparent 40%);
      animation: aurora-flow-2 70s linear infinite;"
  ></div>

  <!-- Layer 3: Biolume & Gold Highlights -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0"
    style="background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 10% 10%, var(--color-stardust-gold) 0%, transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 90% 90%, var(--color-biolume-aqua) 0%, transparent 30%);
      animation: aurora-flow-3 60s linear infinite;"
  ></div>
</div>
